<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-76-0949 </DOCNO><TEXT>This latest addition to the Studies in Geophysics series explores in scientificdetail the phenomenon of lighting, cloud and thunderstorm electricity,and global and regional electrical processes. Consisting of 16 papersby outstanding experts in a number of fields, this volume compiles andreviews many recent advances in such research areas as meteorology, chemistry,electrical engineering, and physics and projects how new knowledge couldbe applied to benefit mankind.</TEXT></DOC>